        <h2>Panel Refresh Controls</h2>
        <p>Enable manual and/or auto refresh of individual dashboard panels.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Configuration-driven panel refresh controls.  Available options include:</li>
          <li>
            <b>refresh.auto.interval</b>- enable auto refresh of a panel; enter the number of seconds</li>
          <li>
            <b>refresh.time.visible</b>- controls the display of the refresh time indicator in the top-right of the panel</li>
          <li>
